					</subparagraph>
          <subparagraph id="HDAF956E0A0754FFCB1208BBDCFA785A8">
            <enum>(B)</enum>
            <text>by inserting after
			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Help America Vote Act of 2002/s:202/p:4">paragraph (4)</cato:entity-ref> the following new paragraph:</text>
						<quoted-block display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H8F499F085ED14B86B5AF10008E371535" style="OLC">
							<paragraph id="H378BCE0BAC1640D4808D2C9972B8A44D">
                <enum>(5)</enum>
                <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">carrying out the duties described in
				subtitle
				E;</text>
							</paragraph>
              <after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block>
            </quoted-block>
					</subparagraph>
        </paragraph>
